Is that an owl?

08:37.602 --> 08:38.602
What?

08:39.534 --> 08:41.433
Oh, yeah.

08:41.434 --> 08:42.535
Can I see it?

08:43.368 --> 08:44.700
Caleb.

08:44.702 --> 08:47.333
Awesome.

08:47.335 --> 08:48.902
You know, that's permanent,
right?

08:50.902 --> 08:52.600
What?

08:52.602 --> 08:53.566
