to cotillion like this?

08:57.901 --> 08:59.334
Language!

08:59.336 --> 09:00.736
You know what else is permanent?

09:01.801 --> 09:02.865
- Family.
- Family?

09:02.867 --> 09:04.800
Family.

09:04.802 --> 09:06.832
Morgan, you're our daughter,
and you always will be.

09:06.834 --> 09:09.432
Nothing can change that.

09:09.434 --> 09:10.967
Your mother is entitled
to show concerns

09:10.969 --> 09:13.666
