you're making about your future.

09:13.668 --> 09:14.866
What affects you
affects all of us.

09:14.868 --> 09:17.533
Okay, James, can we just...
Can we just have breakfast?

09:17.535 --> 09:19.334
- Oh, yeah. Okay, all right.
- Okay? Um...

09:19.336 --> 09:21.299
Morgan, can you just pass
the eggs, please?

09:21.301 --> 09:22.366
Oh, yes. Yes, ma'am.

09:22.368 --> 09:23.935
Thank you so much.

09:27.301 --> 09:28.398
I'll get it.

09:28.400 --> 09:29.565
