playing a prank on us.

10:08.368 --> 10:12.366
"The air is cool,
the season is fall,

10:12.368 --> 10:14.702
soon, Halloween will come
to all."

10:24.501 --> 10:25.800
Is that a Boo?

10:25.802 --> 10:27.433
It's nothing, Caleb.

10:27.435 --> 10:30.267
Uh, nothing looks a hell lot
like a bag of candy.

10:30.269 --> 10:31.701
Let's just eat, okay?

10:34.602 --> 10:39.000
"The air is cool,
the season is fall,

10:39.002 --> 10:42.632
soon, Halloween will come
to all.

10:42.634 --> 10:44.432
Terror and horror,
spooks galore."

10:44.434 --> 10:45.498
Caleb.

10:45.500 --> 10:47.632
"Tricky witches
are at your door."

10:50.236 --> 10:52.799
"The spooks are looking
for things to do.

10:52.801 --> 10:55.599
In fact, one brought this Boo
to you.

10:55.601 --> 10:57.765
The excitement comes
and goes like you,

10:57.767 --> 10:59.769
copy this note and make it two.

11:01.401 --> 11:04.234
