whose places.

11:06.969 --> 11:09.666
But Hallows' Eve
will sure be grand.

11:09.668 --> 11:12.799
Laugh along and follow the plan.

11:12.801 --> 11:15.732
If you fail to pass this Boo,

11:15.734 --> 11:17.835
the spooks will bring your past
to you."

11:24.001 --> 11:25.202
