11:26.667 --> 11:27.733
Yes, sir.

11:27.735 --> 11:29.632
Did you hear me
tell you to stop?

11:29.634 --> 11:31.466
Jesus! He's just messing around.

11:31.468 --> 11:32.800
- Gotta have some fun.
- Uh, no.

11:32.802 --> 11:33.999
It's paganism is what it is.

11:34.001 --> 11:35.699
We don't do Halloween
in this house.

11:35.701 --> 11:36.932
But...

11:36.934 --> 11:38.234
