11:38.236 --> 11:39.399
Excuse me?

11:39.401 --> 11:40.866
It's not a joke.

11:40.868 --> 11:42.203
It's not a prank.

11:43.268 --> 11:44.669
If you don't pass it along,

11:45.300 --> 11:46.932
uh...

11:46.934 --> 11:48.299
It's... it's a curse.

11:48.301 --> 11:49.533
Okay, James,

11:49.535 --> 11:50.799
could you just please just get
that damn thing out of here?

11:50.801 --> 11:52.299
- No. No, don't.
- It's okay.

11:52.301 --> 11:53.866
Sweetie, it's okay. It's okay.

11:53.868 --> 11:55.700
Dude, it's just
a stupid chain letter.

11:55.702 --> 11:57.865
That's something
for the neighborhood moms to do.

11:57.867 --> 12:00.265
There's this kid at school,
Gabe Dawson.

12:00.267 --> 12:02.432
His cousin got a Boo.

12:02.434 --> 12:04.566
When she didn't pass it along,

12:04.568 --> 12:05.999
she died in a bathtub.

12:07.301 --> 12:08.599
Hey!

12:08.601 --> 12:10.966
Morgan, that's not funny.

12:10.968 --> 12:13.933
And there was this,
this, this Vietnam vet,

12:13.935 --> 12:16.266
old guy in the 80s.

12:16.268 --> 12:17.399
All the kids hated him,

12:17.401 --> 12:21.266
so one year, they Booed him
as a joke.

12:21.268 --> 12:23.765
Ghost stories, Caleb.

12:23.767 --> 12:25.966
- But...
- No. No buts.

12:25.968 --> 12:27.565
Give it to me.

12:27.567 --> 12:28.832
That's it.

12:28.834 --> 12:29.935
And you're lighter.

12:31.500 --> 12:32.665
I don't have a lighter.

12:32.667 --> 12:34.298
Yes, you do. There's nothing
that goes on in this house

12:34.300 --> 12:35.633
that I don't know about.
Give it to me.

12:35.635 --> 12:36.733
- Let's go.
- Lighter?

12:36.735 --> 12:37.902
Yes, lighter!

12:41.534 --> 12:42.535
Oh, no!

12:47.969 --> 12:50.733
The only ghost is a Holy Ghost.

12:50.735 --> 12:52.765
The only curse
you need to worry about

12:52.767 --> 12:54.367
is when you take His name
in vain.

12:54.369 --> 12:55.501
Are we clear on that?

12:56.969 --> 12:59.566
I said, "Are we clear on that?"
Crystal?

12:59.568 --> 13:01.536
Crystal.

13:05.701 --> 13:07.201
Have a nice breakfast.

13:09.768 --> 13:11.502
Oh, James.

13:12.434 --> 13:14.398
Oh, god!

13:14.400 --> 13:15.701
Fucking nuts.

