like I was being watched.

18:53.001 --> 18:54.602
Yeah, I know exactly
what you mean.

18:55.234 --> 18:56.766
You do?

18:56.768 --> 18:58.931
Yeah. I don't appreciate it.

18:58.933 --> 19:00.635
You go. I'm trying to get ready.

20:49.234 --> 20:50.335
Okay.

20:51.866 --> 20:52.934
Okay.

22:19.367 --> 22:20.498
Where do you think
you're going?

22:20.500 --> 22:22.764
Oh, shit!

22:22.766 --> 22:25.800
Uh, I'm just gonna head out
and see Ash for a little bit.

22:26.367 --> 22:27.368
Nope.

22:28.700 --> 22:30.468
You're watching Caleb tonight.

22:31.400 --> 22:32.532
