still like go out and have fun.

22:53.767 --> 22:54.935
What about my fun?

22:56.367 --> 22:59.332
You already had yours, remember?

22:59.334 --> 23:00.700
And maybe
a little bit too much.

23:01.967 --> 23:03.765
You're looking at it.

23:03.767 --> 23:05.502
You have no idea
what you're talking about.

23:07.300 --> 23:08.599
I can do the math.

23:08.601 --> 23:10.764
Upstairs, now!

23:10.766 --> 23:12.435
You're not going
anywhere tonight.

23:12.967 --> 23:14.565
Or tomorrow.

23:14.567 --> 23:17.700
Or the day after that,
or the day after that!

23:34.767 --> 23:35.834
Run!

23:45.401 --> 23:47.401
Trick or treat!

23:59.934 --> 24:01.202
Bitch.

24:02.268 --> 24:03.469
