24:06.633 --> 24:07.999
I'm gonna head out, okay?

24:08.001 --> 24:09.269
See Ash for a little bit.

24:10.001 --> 24:12.266
What about the curse?

24:12.268 --> 24:14.931
What if it happens
and I'm here alone?

24:14.933 --> 24:16.965
There is no curse.

24:16.967 --> 24:18.932
Just some lame-ass superstition.

24:18.934 --> 24:20.498
You know, like, uh...

24:20.500 --> 24:21.902
Dad's religious bullshit.

24:22.968 --> 24:24.399
Morgan.

24:25.468 --> 24:27.768
All right, that's... that's him.
I gotta go, okay?

24:29.435 --> 24:32.532
Don't leave.

24:32.534 --> 24:34.599
