24:38.833 --> 24:40.731
they, they don't care anymore...

24:40.733 --> 24:42.634
about each other, about us.

24:43.633 --> 24:44.767
That's not true.

24:48.301 --> 24:49.568
You don't care either.

24:51.234 --> 24:52.665
Why are you doing this to me
right now?

24:52.667 --> 24:54.265
Look...

24:54.267 --> 24:55.665
I do care, okay?

24:55.667 --> 24:58.464
But I care about Ash as well.

24:58.466 --> 24:59.931
Let me go see him
for a few hours,

24:59.933 --> 25:02.765
and then you can, uh,
I don't know watch a movie,

25:02.767 --> 25:04.465
eat some candy.

25:04.467 --> 25:06.299
And, I don't know,
if the doorbell rings,

25:06.301 --> 25:07.800
maybe just don't answer it.

25:08.400 --> 25:09.401
Okay?

25:10.268 --> 25:11.268
Sure.

25:13.334 --> 25:14.497
Be brave, creep.

25:14.499 --> 25:16.699
It's like Freddy Krueger, right?

25:16.701 --> 25:18.535
Curses can't hurt you
if you aren't afraid of 'em.

25:22.566 --> 25:23.764
No.

25:24.833 --> 25:26.301
Morgan, you can't go!

25:56.634 --> 25:57.635
Ash?

26:01.700 --> 26:02.700
Ash?

26:05.234 --> 26:06.298
You know,
this hide-and-seek should...

26:06.300 --> 26:08.468
Oh, shit!

