- What?

26:17.499 --> 26:18.668
Come on, it was a joke.

26:20.566 --> 26:22.534
It's Halloween.

26:22.867 --> 26:23.868
Hey.

26:26.866 --> 26:29.233
Really?

26:29.235 --> 26:30.631
- I...
- I thought I'd be funny.

26:30.633 --> 26:31.698
It's not...

26:31.700 --> 26:33.664
It's not funny. It's funny
when I do it to Caleb.

26:33.666 --> 26:35.301
It's not funny
when you do it to me.

26:35.968 --> 26:37.599
Okay.

26:37.601 --> 26:39.831
Sorry, I just didn't think
you'd be such a pussy about it.

26:39.833 --> 26:41.233
Oh, okay.

26:41.235 --> 26:42.397
You're an asshole.

26:42.399 --> 26:43.898
- Thanks.
- Mm-mm.

26:47.268 --> 26:48.535
Sorry.

26:49.801 --> 26:51.598
It was a joke. I'm sorry.

26:51.600 --> 26:52.898
Jokes are funny.
That was something...

26:52.900 --> 26:54.400
- Oh!
- Okay.

27:02.367 --> 27:04.431
Come on, I was joking.

27:04.433 --> 27:05.500
Okay.

28:05.400 --> 28:06.400
Hey.

28:08.766 --> 28:09.801
Baby.

28:12.500 --> 28:13.564
Come on.

28:13.566 --> 28:14.767
You still pissed at me?

28:20.434 --> 28:21.433
Morgan.

28:24.767 --> 28:25.868
No, Ash.

28:27.001 --> 28:28.535
I'm not pissed at you.

28:29.533 --> 28:30.767
You know me. I'm...

28:31.800 --> 28:33.367
pissed at everyone.

28:34.633 --> 28:36.567
Okay, well...

28:37.934 --> 28:39.735
Well, let's just go
and have some fun, okay?

30:15.800 --> 30:17.297
Trick or treat!

30:20.667 --> 30:22.268
Asshole!

31:23.334 --> 31:24.701
So you wanna talk to me now?

31:28.300 --> 31:29.835
Listen, I know something's up...

31:31.733 --> 31:34.297
'cause your ring
is dark as hell.

31:34.299 --> 31:35.300
Yeah.

31:36.000 --> 31:38.264
I'm no color expert,

31:38.266 --> 31:39.564
but I can only imagine

31:39.566 --> 31:41.233
pitch black
doesn't mean you're happy.

31:43.366 --> 31:45.668
Or... horny.

31:50.500 --> 31:52.268
Or whatever it is.

31:53.533 --> 31:54.767
I got the cure.

31:57.766 --> 32:00.664
Yeah, but it just cures
the sickness,

32:00.666 --> 32:02.464
not the disease.

32:02.466 --> 32:03.934
What? So you got a disease now?

32:06.633 --> 32:07.934
My family is.

32:09.634 --> 32:11.635
Uh, what are you talking about?

32:13.334 --> 32:15.732
I don't know, just...

32:15.734 --> 32:17.999
something Caleb said earlier,
I guess.

32:18.001 --> 32:18.801
Caleb?

32:20.867 --> 32:23.832
Mouthy little fucker.

32:23.834 --> 32:25.535
Yeah. He's a little fucker.

32:27.967 --> 32:29.699
But he...

32:29.701 --> 32:31.835
he notices things, you know?

32:36.266 --> 32:37.865
What about your mom?

32:37.867 --> 32:39.401
You know,
we never talk about her.

32:40.600 --> 32:42.233
Oh, 'cause she doesn't exist.

32:43.467 --> 32:44.535
Not anymore.

32:48.000 --> 32:49.434
That must be nice.

32:51.400 --> 32:52.798
What?

32:52.800 --> 32:54.631
No.

32:54.633 --> 32:56.298
No, trust me.

32:56.300 --> 32:57.568
Not having a mom sucks.

33:00.500 --> 33:02.634
I meant the non-existing.

33:04.367 --> 33:05.497
Don't.

33:05.499 --> 33:06.500
Okay.

33:07.333 --> 33:08.632
I mean it.

33:08.634 --> 33:10.532
Jesus, I was fucking joking.

33:10.534 --> 33:12.234
- I'm not!
- Phew.

33:13.866 --> 33:15.331
I love you.

33:17.766 --> 33:20.233
Oh, why does it bother you
so much when I say it?

33:21.299 --> 33:22.599
Means I'm not ready to say it.

33:22.601 --> 33:23.601
Then don't.

33:24.833 --> 33:25.964
I'm not forcing you to.

33:25.966 --> 33:28.632
We're just talking about me.

33:28.634 --> 33:30.601
Yeah, but it's not
just something you say.

33:30.999 --> 33:32.200
I know.

33:35.567 --> 33:37.201
It's something that you feel...

33:38.932 --> 33:40.367
for a while.

33:43.467 --> 33:44.668
And then you don't.

33:46.733 --> 33:47.768
And then...

33:48.567 --> 33:49.601
you're stuck.

33:54.266 --> 33:55.400
Yeah.

33:56.466 --> 33:57.467
I don't know.

34:00.234 --> 34:02.268
I mean, you're not thinking
like one day...

34:05.333 --> 34:06.432
I guess, I just shouldn't...

34:06.434 --> 34:08.500
I guess I just wouldn't mind
being stuck with you.

34:10.333 --> 34:11.567
Stupid, I know.

34:13.333 --> 34:16.600
Like would being stuck with me
be so bad.

34:19.632 --> 34:20.701
I just...

34:21.766 --> 34:23.467
I don't know. I...

34:24.666 --> 34:26.565
I gotta get out here.

34:26.567 --> 34:30.664
I can't take another four years
of this house, I swear to God,

34:30.666 --> 34:32.931
of Mom's drinking and...

34:32.933 --> 34:35.231
Dad's fire and brimstone shit.

34:35.233 --> 34:36.368
You'll get out.

34:38.567 --> 34:40.799
What if I just wasn't
good enough,

34:40.801 --> 34:42.431
like I don't get in anywhere...

34:42.433 --> 34:44.398
You worry too much, baby.

34:44.400 --> 34:46.831
Hey, did I ever...
Did I ever mention that to you?

34:48.367 --> 34:49.368
Maybe.

34:51.266 --> 34:54.764
You're so beautiful,
and you're smart.

