40:11.434 --> 40:13.997
That this is real.

40:13.999 --> 40:15.534
You and I are real.

40:16.665 --> 40:18.333
Oh, so it's not...

40:19.500 --> 40:20.664
Mm-mm.

40:20.666 --> 40:21.730
- No.
- No?

40:21.732 --> 40:23.631
No.

40:23.633 --> 40:25.766
So I was thinking I was gonna
get an "M" right here.

40:27.434 --> 40:29.764
Like, uh, be like Joe Pesci
in <i>Home Alone.</i>

40:29.766 --> 40:30.830
Yeah, yeah, I mean...

40:30.832 --> 40:32.533
- Yeah?
- Sure, whatever.

40:36.732 --> 40:39.331
<i>Hey.</i>

40:39.333 --> 40:40.664
<i>You'll be okay.</i>

40:40.666 --> 40:41.964
What the fuck!

40:41.966 --> 40:43.730
What the fuck are you doing?

40:43.732 --> 40:45.598
- I need to go home, right now.
- It's all right.

40:45.600 --> 40:46.897
It's...

40:46.899 --> 40:47.933
What?

40:48.733 --> 40:50.298
It's fine.

40:50.300 --> 40:51.332
- I want to go home now!
- Are you...

40:51.334 --> 40:53.631
Okay, okay, okay.
Look, it's okay, it's real.

40:53.633 --> 40:54.498
Look at your hand.

40:54.500 --> 40:56.831
- I wanna go right now!
- Okay, let's go.

40:56.833 --> 40:57.897
Fuck.

40:57.899 --> 40:58.900
Morgan.

42:32.933 --> 42:35.730
"And if any mischief follow,

42:35.732 --> 42:37.998
