42:38.000 --> 42:39.534
an eye for an eye,

42:40.432 --> 42:41.866
a tooth for a tooth."

42:44.299 --> 42:45.333
Oh.

43:08.565 --> 43:11.731
"A hand for a hand,
a foot for a foot,

43:11.733 --> 43:13.867
burning for burning,
