44:25.967 --> 44:27.168
Shit.

44:48.699 --> 44:49.733
Reggie?

44:55.266 --> 44:56.267
Reggie!

45:03.298 --> 45:04.299
Reggie?

45:10.433 --> 45:13.297
Reggie, Reggie.

45:13.299 --> 45:14.633
What's wrong, baby?

45:15.866 --> 45:17.766
He died.

45:19.433 --> 45:20.533
